      <title>波兰决策者对央行行长 2026 年的赌注表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/polish-policymakers-cast-doubt-on-central-bank-chief-s-2026-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多位波兰央行行长表示，随着通胀回落，他们可能在明年开始考虑降息，而央行行长亚当格拉宾斯基 (Adam Glapinski) 出人意料地表示，将宽松预期延长至 2026 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/polish-policymakers-cast-doubt-on-central-bank-chief-s-2026-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 14:31:49 GMT</pubDate>
